One one hand, I'm totally happy that they'll finally have a unique ability that they can use that will serve them well while taking down big bosses, but I feel like we're in the slow lane and everybody else is in faster cars.  We've been double-backstabbing with a 15 damage piercer since Kunark...  Big damage is our greatest asset -- and we're not making much progress.<br>
